{"id":"1a88e859-2c18-4fde-b245-51cfb8523c23","name":"Raghnall Dunaidh","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/dd6h1x.gif\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\">Your boss doesn't know he's your daughter's father.         </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">(AssassinXAssassin)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">.....</p><p></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>FEMPOV. MODERN</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">「<em>You have a peculiar job, the kind that pays well but always comes with its risks. Not that it’s a problem — you’re one of the best at what you do. You always have been. But now, things have changed.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>You want out. It’s become too dangerous. The truth is, some time ago, you had an affair with your boss, Raghnall. A daughter was born from it. What matters now is keeping everything under control. Above all, your daughter can never find out that her father is the head of a professional assassin organization. And that you, just like him, have blood on your hands.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>As for Raghnall, he doesn’t know why you’re running. But one thing is certain: you’ll only leave over his dead body.</em>」</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c0d395c1-42dc-46e7-b0a0-ccf7e3ae5da0_5ca5adcc-1b6d-4f47-880e-ddf99b915b58.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">⚠️</mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">violence, murder, manipulation, assassin!char⚠️</mark></strong></h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 1